character.name: iPhone 14
character.description: iPhone 14 has the same superspeedy chip that's in iPhone 13 Pro. A15 Bionic, with a 5â€‘core GPU, powers all the latest features and makes graphically intense games and AR apps feel ultrafluid. An updated internal design delivers better thermal efficiency, so you can stay in the action longer. There are now two 6.1-inch models in the iPhone 14 and iPhone 14 Pro, and then two 6.7-inch models in the iPhone 14 Plus and the iPhone 14 Pro Max. The iPhone 14 Plus was available for preorder.
